            <span>Open a <strong class="text-zec-text">terminal</strong> and navigate to where you downloaded the file</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-zec-yellow font-bold text-xs mt-0.5 shrink-0">2</span>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
